<emphasis id="B3A80EA0CF7DC6250BFC98E7E146F79F" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Distinguished by the narrow linear-lanceolate, glabrous sepals.
</paragraph>
